COMMENDATIONS. Commending Chennault International Airport on the occasion of its
40th Anniversary.
1 A RESOLUTION
2 To commend Chennault International Airport on the occasion of its 40th anniversary.
3 WHEREAS, over the past forty years, Chennault International Airport has evolved
4 into a nationally recognized aviation hub known for excellence in maintenance, repair,
5 overhaul, and innovation; and
6 WHEREAS, the airport has proven itself to be a significant creator of new jobs,
7 providing thousands of high-quality employment opportunities by consistently attracting
8 leading aviation and non-aviation companies as on-site business partners, while fostering
9 investment and strengthening the regional economy; and
10 WHEREAS, Chennault International Airport proudly continues its distinguished
11 military heritage as a former Strategic Air Command base and remains an active training and
12 exercise site for B-52 Stratofortress aircraft and other military aviation operations; and
13 WHEREAS, the airport has contributed to the resilience and diversification of the
14 local economy, supporting growth beyond traditional industries; and
15 WHEREAS, Chennault International Airport has demonstrated a strong commitment
16 to workforce development through partnerships with local college training programs; and
17 WHEREAS, the leadership, on-site businesses, and workforce of the Chennault
18 International Airport have exhibited dedication, innovation, and vision, ensuring its
